{"questionId":"3514926","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Another player catches the basketball when it is at a height of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn></math> metres.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> when this player catches the basketball.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>correct sketch of quadratic function and a straight line in approximate correct position&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/d89a6237d1c7d1e26da82432523b622be309e6a0.png\"></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>88</mn></math> (seconds) (<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>87577</mn><mo>…</mo></math> (seconds))&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p>setting the equation equal to 1.2&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>75</mn><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>75</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>2</mn></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>88</mn></math> (seconds) (<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>87577</mn><mo>…</mo></math> (seconds))&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>(M1)A0</strong></em> if <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0336702</mn><mo>…</mo></math> seen as (part of) a final answer.</p>\n<p>Award <em><strong>M1A0</strong></em> for answer of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>9</mn></math> seen without working.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"3514926","referenceCode":"23M.1.SL.TZ2.10c","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the value of t when this player catches the basketball.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"c","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.5—Modelling functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.6—Modelling skills"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}